When Justice Becomes Code — shrinking the Discretion Gap (DG)

Same facts + rules, different outcomes = DG.
LC/FG compute the rule-pure baseline (Y★).
LCa/JC show where discretion creates variance (Y ≠ Y★).

5-step DG harness:
	1.	Compute Y★ (LC). 2) Put it in a Proposed Order.
	2.	Pinpoint evidence + TOA (validated).
	3.	Capture the ruling (Y). 5) Log the gap (+ doctrine).

